title: IMF Revives Greek Euro-Exit Warning Amid Deadlocked Bailout Talks - WSJ
text:
WASHINGTON—The International Monetary Fund warned on Tuesday that Greece once again risks a eurozone exit amid stalled bailout talks, sending the clearest signal yet the emergency lender isn’t likely to soon rejoin Europe’s failed efforts to fix the debt-weary nation.
